Vaz, Jacinto : (zolm' : 27 epril 1919, manddur).

Namnecho kantarist (gaik), ani lokpriy tiatrist (nattkokar). Tacho bapuy krastto vajh ho boro tiatr digdorxok axil'lo. Tachem mollavem xikop manddurak zalem. Mukhauyolem' xikxonn gheupakhatir tannem mumboichea chondnovaddi littol fleaur skulant provex ghetlo. Bhurgeponnasaun to kantaram (podam) rochtalo. Skulachea pracharean kantarist mhonnun taka poilo voilo machyer haddlo. Fuddem tannem tiatramni lhan - vhodd bhumika korpak survat keli. Pirayechea 27vea vorsa 'hamv tuzo ghorkar' hea tiatrant ek mukhel bhumika korun tannem lokancheo modro aple votten oddun ghetleo. Survek tannem gombhir bhumika keleo. Punn fuddarak to vinodi nott mhonnun mukhar ailo. Dioginyu d melo hannem taka 1960t goyant haddlo. 'xeutt obru chukotleach' ho tacho tiatr boroch gajlo. Apleak favo toxo vinodi bhumika mellnat tem polloun tannem svotach vinodi tiatr boroupak survat keli, ani eka fattofatt 28 tiatr boroun machyer haddle. Te borech gajle ani tachea kamachi tust - tokhnnai zali. 1959t tacho 'kunead ani mana' ho tiatr soglleank manoulo. Uprant tannem to tiatr afrikent mombasa, nairobi, nakas, aruxa, tangania, moxi, darusalom' hanga vhorun tache 24 proyog kele. 1976t tannem barin, kuvett, oman, moskot hea akhati dexamni aple tiatr vhorun zoitiunt kele.

'Amchem Noxib', 'mhoji ghorkan'n', hea konknni sinemantleo vinodi bhumika korun prekxokankoddlean taka vhodd tokhnnai mell'llea.

Lokamni taka 'tiatristancho raza' oxi podvi dili. Chikatten tannem machyechi sadhna korun gõychea gamvam konnkonnim aple tiatr dakhoile. Modim 7 vorsam tannem 'omisara d gova' mhollear akaxovanni ponnji kendrar nokri keli. Nokre uprant porot tannem aplem lokx tiatracher kendrit kelem. Aizomeren tachea tiatranche 5 hozamrauyor proyog zaleat. Titlyai proyogant tannem bhumikai keleat. Tannem sumar 2 hozar kantaram rochleant. Ech.Em'. Vhi kompnin tachea kantaracheo dhvonimudrika kaddleat ani teo boreoch gajleat.

Gõy kola okadomi ani sinettaims (prokaxon somstha) hanche purskar tannem zoddleant. Mumboichea sinettaimsan taka 'konknni palkacho charli chaplin' tor ttaims ef inddian 'keameddicho raza' oxem pacharun tachi tust-tokhnnai kelea.

